WEBVTT

1
00:00:01.400 --> 00:00:02.200
Ah!

2
00:00:02.733 --> 00:00:04.466
Hey, are you alright?

3
00:00:04.533 --> 00:00:06.400
Sit here for a while

4
00:00:08.100 --> 00:00:08.966
Be careful

5
00:00:10.266 --> 00:00:11.700
This flat foot has been broken for a long time

6
00:00:11.700 --> 00:00:13.066
The shoes must not fit.

7
00:00:13.066 --> 00:00:14.033
Wait a minute.

8
00:00:20.666 --> 00:00:23.066
Come and try on these shoes.

9
00:00:33.866 --> 00:00:35.766
How does it fit?

10
00:00:35.766 --> 00:00:36.900
It fits perfectly.

11
00:00:37.466 --> 00:00:40.133
I didn't expect my daughter's shoes to fit you well.

12
00:00:40.133 --> 00:00:42.400
Ah, those are your daughter's shoes?

13
00:00:42.400 --> 00:00:45.566
How much is that? I'll give you the money, so I don't need to give it to you.

14
00:00:46.466 --> 00:00:49.300
By the way, do you have any children?

15
00:00:49.300 --> 00:00:50.700
I have kids.

16
00:00:51.066 --> 00:00:54.633
Is it convenient for me to leave your contact information?

17
00:00:54.666 --> 00:00:56.566
For so many years, I have been raising children alone

18
00:00:56.700 --> 00:00:59.666
I would like to discuss this daughter's education with you

19
00:00:59.666 --> 00:01:01.033
Ah eat

20
00:01:01.366 --> 00:01:02.933
Yeah, OK.

